<plot>As the star of the television series "Black/Jack" in the mid-1970s, Benjamin Beane was the world's biggest TV star. However, seven years and one permanent hiatus later, Benjamin is a washed up has-been who can't let go of his fading stardom or his former co-star... a felt puppet named Jack. When Jack is stolen by an eccentric drug dealer, Benjamin embarks on a rescue mission with an unlikely friend that will force him to decide, once and for all, to either hold tight to his past or to take control of his future.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?231194</url></doc>
